<cl=A2A2A2>
<tab>Barbarians are great warriors who have dedicated themselves to an acient cult of power and fury. Both military and magical achievements are appreciated in this guild and those who are not good at both will have it rough here. Barbarians possess great strength, but they are not too dexterous. Only brute force attracts them, therefore Barbarians prefer earth as the most powerful of the four elements. Secrect skills of this guild match Barbarians' strength: they can go berserker and stun the enemy, so he is incapable of either seeing or fighting. Using special magic, they also can cause damage to the enemy at a significant range as if he were next to them.
<br>
<br>
<l="hts:\\language\guilds.hts">See guild descriptions<\l><br>
